   <title><![CDATA[Law and Cosmology—The Folly of Alternatives to God-Based Legal Systems [God, Law, and Liberty]]]></title>
   <link>https://app.dropwave.io/episode/bdd295af-96de-4481-a134-12685524b9ff/law-and-cosmology-the-folly-of-alternatives-to-god-based-legal-systems.mp3</link>
   <description><![CDATA[<p>This week, David begins to examine the alternatives to a Christian based legal system that mankind has come up with and how the late Yale law professor Arthur Leff, an atheist, debunks them as non-authoritative and unworkable. Leff provides great insight into what he calls a search for the &ldquo;metaphorical equivalent&rdquo; to the God of the Bible.</p>]]></description>
